      "content": "# useSelectedDocument hook is auto-generated per document model\n\nFor each document model, the system generates a corresponding hook:\n\n- `Todo` model → `useSelectedTodoDocument`\n- `Invoice` model → `useSelectedInvoiceDocument`\n- `ServiceOffering` model → `useSelectedServiceOfferingDocument`\n\nThese hooks are generated in `editors/hooks/` and return `[document, dispatch]`. Never implement them manually — they follow a specific pattern that matches the document model's type system.\n\nSince [[editors use the modern React hooks pattern from reactor-browser]], these hooks are the standard entry point for all editor components.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[editor patterns]]\n- [[model-editor wiring]]",
